        GREETINGS_TRAVELER_I_AM_A_RESISTANCE_OFFICER_WHOSE                     = 7382,  -- Greetings, traveler. I am a resistance officer whose charge is the procurement of cruor. If you would be willing to part with any cruor you possess, I will issue you with helpful items in return.
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_CRUOR_BALANCE_NOTHING_LEARN                           = 7383,  -- What will you do? (Cruor balance: #) Nothing. Learn about cruor. Exchange for items. Exchange for temporary items. Exchange for key items. Exchange for enhancement effects. Dispose of abyssite.
