        KNOWN_BY_SOME_AS_BLOOD_GOLD_THESE_RED                                  = 7385,  -- Known by some as blood gold, these red granules are highly prized and see use as both energy source and construction material.
        IT_WOULD_BE_NO_EXAGGERATION_TO_SAY_THAT                                = 7386,  -- It would be no exaggeration to say that cruor is the lifeblood of the resistance effort. As a matter of fact, the bulk of items I have in stock are cruor-based.
