        WELL_MET_WAYFARER_I_AM_AN_ATMA_INFUSIONIST                             = 7432,  -- Well met, wayfarer. I am an Atma Infusionist, and from my title I trust you can glean my field of expertise. Those who possess % may come to me to have atma infused.
        HOW_MIGHT_I_SERVE_YOU_YOU_MAY_NOT                                      = 7433,  -- How might I serve you? You may not. Tell me about atma. Infuse me with atma. Examine infused atma. Purge atma. Reinfuse previous atma set. Select from recent history.
        ATMA_IS_MOST_ACCURATELY_DESCRIBED_AS_THE_CRYSTALLINE                   = 7434,  -- Atma is most accurately described as the crystalline agglomeration of an Abyssean creature's soul. Through painstaking research, we infusionists have discovered a way to imbue ordinary people such as yourself with its power.
        INFUSION_MAKES_POSSIBLE_THE_AUGMENTATION_OF_INDIVIDUALS_GRANTING       = 7435,  -- Infusion makes possible the augmentation of individuals, granting them powers particular to the creature from which the atma is sourced.
        THE_INFUSION_PROCESS_REQUIRES_THREE_OBJECTS_AN_ATMA                    = 7436,  -- The infusion process requires three objects: an atma, %, and cruor.
        IS_A_RARE_VARIETY_OF_ANCIENT_ABYSSITE_THAT                             = 7437,  -- % is a rare variety of ancient abyssite that can only be procured with great difficulty. And it won't please you to know that atma is rarer still.
        FOR_ONLY_THE_MOST_SAVAGE_CREATURES_YOU_SEE                             = 7438,  -- For only the most savage creatures, you see, are known to yield atma. And if you thought that weren't trial enough, only by employing special combat strategies will atma be yours to own.
        ATMA_YIELDING_MONSTERS_ARE_KNOWN_TO_HAVE_VULNERABILITIES               = 7439,  -- Atma-yielding monsters are known to have vulnerabilities that, if exploited, may result in a swift end to the confrontation.
        STRIKE_AT_A_FOE_S_WEAKNESS_AND_IT                                      = 7440,  -- Strike at a foe's weakness, and it will drop different spoils, often more valuable than usual. Among them you may find atma.
        THE_VULNERABILITIES_CAN_BROADLY_BE_DIVIDED_INTO_THREE                  = 7441,  -- The vulnerabilities can broadly be divided into three categories: magic attacks, physical-based weapon skills, and magic-based weapon skills.
        FOR_INSTANCE_THERE_ARE_MONSTERS_KNOWN_TO_BE                            = 7442,  -- For instance, there are monsters known to be weak against magic-based weapon skills. Inflicting such damage upon them will impair their movement, and you may consequently be rewarded with atma.
        ALL_LIVING_CREATURES_HOWEVER_POSSESS_THE_CAPACITY_TO                   = 7443,  -- All living creatures, however, possess the capacity to adapt, and vulnerabilities have been observed to change. Be wary if you wish not to discover to your sorrow that a once-foolproof strategy no longer applies.
        BESTING_SUCH_FELL_CREATURES_IS_IN_ITSELF_A                             = 7444,  -- Besting such fell creatures is in itself a harrowing task, and becomes even more so if procuring atma is your objective.
        BUT_SHOULD_FORTUNE_SMILE_UPON_YOU_AND_YOU                              = 7445,  -- But should fortune smile upon you and you find yourself in possession of atma, bring it here. I will see that it serves you well.
        WHICH_ATMA_WILL_YOU_HAVE_INFUSED_NONE_FOR                              = 7446,  -- Which atma will you have infused? None for now. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. %. Previous page. Next page.
        CRUOR_IS_REQUIRED_TO_INFUSE_THE                                        = 7447,  -- # cruor is required to infuse the %.
