        YOU_WILL_OBSERVE_THAT_MARTELLOS_HAVE_BEEN_CONSTRUCTED                  = 8119,  -- You will observe that martellos have been constructed in numerous locales, so as to provide strategically located safe havens for harried resistance fighters. No doubt you will find yourself making use of them as well.
