        THAT_BEING_THE_CASE_WE_RE_IN_CONTINUAL                                 = 8122,  -- That being the case, we're in continual need of volunteers willing to take on the vital task of replenishing these martellos.
        I_HAVE_BEEN_CHARGED_WITH_OVERSEEING_A_SUPPLY                           = 8123,  -- I have been charged with overseeing a supply of martello fuel. Should you be willing to take part in a replenishment run, you need only say the word. Needless to say, you will not go unrewarded for your efforts.
